    "The Museum was late to purchase the work of the New York abstract expressionists even though they lived and exhibited in the shadow of the museum.": [],
    "As a museum director, he instituted aggressive advertising campaigns for the museum at a time when few other art museums did, insisting that exhibition catalogs be accessible both financially and intellectually to the public.": [],
